      "cookedHtml": "<p>Please post your reviews, feedback, issues, questions about the app here.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Supercharge Your Workflow with Google Drive Integration in <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Seamlessly connect your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> workspace with Google Drive to upload, preview, and manage files—all without switching platforms!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Boost collaboration, ensure file version control, and streamline project management for your team.</p>\n<p>See it in action! <a href=\"https://calendly.com/atul31gupta\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Schedule a demo</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/key.png?v=12\" title=\":key:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":key:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Key Features:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/outbox_tray.png?v=12\" title=\":outbox_tray:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":outbox_tray:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Upload Files to Google Drive from <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/file_folder.png?v=12\" title=\":file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Effortlessly upload documents, images, spreadsheets, and presentations to Google Drive directly from your boards.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Stay productive without leaving the platform!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrows_counterclockwise.png?v=12\" title=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automatic Sync</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/stopwatch.png?v=12\" title=\":stopwatch:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":stopwatch:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Keep your files up-to-date with real-time sync between <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> and Google Drive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Any changes are instantly reflected, ensuring your team always works on the latest versions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/card_index_dividers.png?v=12\" title=\":card_index_dividers:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":card_index_dividers:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Organize and Manage Files Efficiently</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/pushpin.png?v=12\" title=\":pushpin:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":pushpin:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automatically create board-level and item-level folders in Google Drive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/dart.png?v=12\" title=\":dart:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":dart:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Easily organize, create new folders, and manage files—all within <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>—keeping everything neat and accessible.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/handshake.png?v=12\" title=\":handshake:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":handshake:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Real-Time Collaboration</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Collaborate on Google Docs, Sheets, and Slides directly from <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=12\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Share files with your team and experience real-time updates, enhancing teamwork and productivity.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/closed_lock_with_key.png?v=12\" title=\":closed_lock_with_key:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":closed_lock_with_key:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Backup &amp; Security</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/shield.png?v=12\" title=\":shield:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":shield:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Rely on Google Drive’s robust backup and security features for peace of mind.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/busts_in_silhouette.png?v=12\" title=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":busts_in_silhouette:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Manage file access and keep sensitive data secure within your workspace.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/open_book.png?v=12\" title=\":open_book:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_book:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Need More Details?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Check out our <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vTaTqSHPFY4ohXnw7dMFwkawdBoos60bmS1yrvdwWwYNErqE4ZPEE1TJcydRT0lC52mOPKAqzYWZ14p/pub\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">complete app documentation</a> for in-depth guidance</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/point_right.png?v=12\" title=\":point_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":point_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Get started today and unlock the full potential!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/speech_balloon.png?v=12\" title=\":speech_balloon:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":speech_balloon:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> For any feedback, suggestions, or queries, feel free to contact us at <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/email.png?v=12\" title=\":email:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":email:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"mailto:apps@cloudvandana.com\">apps@cloudvandana.com</a>.</p>"
